        </dl>

        <dl style="background-color:darkslategray; margin-top:2%; padding-left:10px; padding-right:10px; box-shadow:5px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.5); border:solid 2px black;">
            <dt class="col-sm-6">
                <span style="font-size:20px; text-decoration:underline; padding-bottom:5px;">Top 5 Counties for Sightings</span>
            </dt>
            <dd class="col-sm-12">
                <span style="font-size:17px; font-weight:600;">
                    #1 Collier: 21
                </span><br />
                Most Recent: November 2012, (Class A) - Daylight sighting of a man-like ape while target shooting in the Big Cypress National Preserve
            </dd>
            <dd class="col-sm-12">
                <span style="font-size:17px; font-weight:600;">
                    #2 Marion: 19
                </span><br />
                Most Recent: August 2017 (Class A) - Multiple witnesses, daylight sighting, Hopkins Prairie, Ocala NF, next to Florida Trail
            </dd>
            <dd class="col-sm-12">
                <span style="font-size:17px; font-weight:600;">
                    #3 Lake: 18
                </span><br />
                Most Recent: November 2015 (Class A) - Tall hairy figure is seen by the roadside on SR-19 near Altoona
            </dd>
            <dd class="col-sm-12">
                <span style="font-size:17px; font-weight:600;">
                    #4 Polk: 18
                </span><br />
                August 2017 (Class B) - Large brown figure seen standing in water near Lake Wales
            </dd>
            <dd class="col-sm-12">
                <span style="font-size:17px; font-weight:600;">
                    #5 Clay: 16
                </span><br />
